dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Manitowoc County, Wisconsin in 2015.[Centerline is a linear feature class that represents roads in Manitowoc County, Wisconsin. It contains the low-to-high address ranges for both the left and right sides of roads. This feature class may contain actual high and low or theoretical high and low addresses depending on how the municipality reported their values.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
